     <div type="poem">
   <head>Upon the matter of
the work.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>TAke so much <hi>Ru<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="3 letters">
               <desc>•••</desc>
            </gap>b,</hi> learned <hi>Galen</hi> sayes;</l>
      <l>Take so much <hi>Cassia,</hi> so much <hi>Aloes,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>So much of th' other, <hi>Ana</hi>
         <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap> of such and such.</l>
      <l>Give me this RECIPE, <hi>Take not too much.</hi>
      </l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>WHat e're the Doctour gives, he does put
to it</l>
      <l>
         <hi>
            <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>asting:</hi> Take this, and fast; and it will do it.</l>
      <l>
         <hi>See!</hi> without <gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>asting Physick can cure none:</l>
      <l>But Fasting will cure almost all, alone.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
